		<h1 class="title">现实要被虚拟到什么程度才够？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">李如一</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-02-01 07:51:26 +0800"></span>
